{"type": "article", "id": 14443, "title": "哪怕一年有三季赏不了樱花，这房子也值得一住", "description": "这种孤独感，可能恰好和日本的审美意识相契合吧。", "date": "2015-09-05T08:27:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 15498, "name": "私宅"}, {"id": 15499, "name": "日本乡下"}, {"id": 8530, "name": "樱花"}, {"id": 15500, "name": "赏樱之家"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 139, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605213702smUgeHEAySOaBXuF.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是<a href=\"http://www.gooood.hk/house-reflecting-ripples.htm\" target=\"_blank\">位于日本茨城县筑波市的一个孤独的赏樱之家</a>。这栋住宅名叫波纹住宅，在有樱花的一侧，建筑师开了一个内院，既能观赏到樱花，也为每个房间带来了充足的照明。从外观上来看，房子有着纯白色的外墙和三进式的房门，在樱花烂漫的季节，屋主人可以在巨大的落地窗前赏花。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t我只想说，房主，你开放 Airbnb 吗？\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t樱花期稍纵即逝，在无樱可赏的季节，这房子恐怕会显得很孤独，<span>不过这种孤独感，也恰好和日本的审美意识相契合吧。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213652OT3jCQhEYSqInt5b.jpg\" title=\"“樱花之家”的远景\" alt=\"“樱花之家”的远景\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>“樱花之家”的远景</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213653WajrquZeFli6cnf5.jpg\" title=\"三层白色外墙\" alt=\"三层白色外墙\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>三层白色外墙</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060521365347KwPsEvuxfBhpCt.jpg\" title=\"近看房子\" alt=\"近看房子\" data-ratio=\"0.7375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>近看房子</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213654yKAMGWZPQDN0YjJn.jpg\" title=\"整面的落地窗适合赏樱\" alt=\"整面的落地窗适合赏樱\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>整面的落地窗适合赏樱</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213654eJFU5aucqs426WKV.jpg\" title=\"屋子的另一个角度\" alt=\"屋子的另一个角度\" data-ratio=\"0.7375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>屋子的另一个角度</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213655sF6Cn80DOImXaYAq.jpg\" title=\"室内设计\" alt=\"室内设计\" data-ratio=\"0.7375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>室内设计</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213655Kd8xW3Y2UB60c5Xv.jpg\" title=\"起居室\" alt=\"起居室\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>起居室</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060521365681lwbVymkPUc3TFi.jpg\" title=\"餐厅及二楼的空间\" alt=\"餐厅及二楼的空间\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>餐厅及二楼的空间</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213656kWl2iCZPzoKO5wHh.jpg\" title=\"走廊及院外\" alt=\"走廊及院外\" data-ratio=\"0.7375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>走廊及院外</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213657qQCeOFIvm6fc2gRi.jpg\" title=\"空旷的房间\" alt=\"空旷的房间\" data-ratio=\"0.8140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>空旷的房间</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213657sZpeGntHArTamPv8.jpg\" title=\"二楼俯视视角\" alt=\"二楼俯视视角\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>二楼俯视视角</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213658H0ukNa1dmj4gr5ni.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213658YgKQ10Bdiq2cpyo6.jpg\" title=\"洗手间\" alt=\"洗手间\" data-ratio=\"0.7375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>洗手间</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052136599WHxjbVYaMKDJs8c.jpg\" title=\"夜间远景\" alt=\"夜间远景\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>夜间远景</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t这座房子是由建筑事务所 <a href=\"http://kichi-d.com/\">Kichi Architectural Design</a> 设计完成的，这是一家日本的建筑事务所，他们的作品颇具东方的禅意，比如这个位于日本农村的住宅：\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213659sZyEFR7WMDX6tqnH.jpg\" title=\"犹抱琵琶半遮面\" alt=\"犹抱琵琶半遮面\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>犹抱琵琶半遮面</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213700NzGXQvTF3dHMgDcy.jpg\" title=\"乡下住宅的另一个角度\" alt=\"乡下住宅的另一个角度\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>乡下住宅的另一个角度</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213700tFXRkCyzAqLZE3xV.jpg\" title=\"另一处民宅\" alt=\"另一处民宅\" data-ratio=\"0.60625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>另一处民宅</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213701euoiJ0lkHmnLEjhX.jpg\" title=\"另外一个住宅作品\" alt=\"另外一个住宅作品\" data-ratio=\"0.6515625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>另外一个住宅作品</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213701qN9skjb54eaAOfYd.jpg\" title=\"他们专注于在日本乡下设计私宅\" alt=\"他们专注于在日本乡下设计私宅\" data-ratio=\"0.65625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>他们专注于在日本乡下设计私宅</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span><em>题图来源：</em><a href=\"http://www.gooood.hk/house-reflecting-ripples.htm\" target=\"_blank\"><em>gooood</em><em></em></a></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}